Monitoring Kubernetes Cluster using Prometheus and Grafana hands-on project. We will accomplish it by completing each task in the project:

Task 1: To create a single node kubernetes cluster using kind which is a tool for running local Kubernetes clusters using Docker containers as nodes on Ubuntu OS cloud workspace.

Cluster Creation Steps
Step#1: First we will create a cluster using:

kind create cluster

Step#2: Check cluster

kind get clusters

Step#3: Get cluster info

kubectl cluster-info

Step#5: Check Nodes

kubectl get nodes

Step#6: Check All

kubectl get all -A
